Super Mario Bros. is incredibly common and has an 8 KiB CHR ROM. It is shipped on the NROM-256 board.<br /><br />Super Mario Bros. and Duck Hunt is also incredibly common and has a 16 KiB CHR ROM. It is shipped on a GNROM-compatible board.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=9">tepples</a> — Sun Mar 25, 2007 3:35 pm</p><hr />
